Megaton took the discs and placed them in the dragons mouth in the 
back of his robotic head. "If I have my way the Maximals inside will 
end up the same way Yessss" Looking at Megatrons bot form was like 
looking into a funhouse mirror, the predacon leader was smaller but 
esentially had the same face. The mutant started running the 
information through his mind trying to devise a plan of attack worthy 
of the diabolical leader of the Predacons.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, JP3884@a... wrote:
>     Megatron raises his arm and a small disk slides out of a stored 
> compatment. He hands it to Megaton. "All the information on the 
ship is here, 
> although I think from the long assult from the Allience it should 
be a pile 
> of ruble by now."
